### Login (get token) - 登入取得 token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{adminUser}}",
  "password": "{{adminPass}}"
}

> {% client.global.set("token", response.body.token); %}

### List all orders - 列出全部訂單
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List by status (CANCELLED / CONFIRMED / COMPLETED / PENDING) - 依狀態篩選
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/orders?status=CANCELLED
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update order status (replace 1 with real order id) - 更新訂單狀態
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/orders/1/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "CONFIRMED"
}
